&lt;li&gt;Collaborate closely with ML researchers, product teams, and other platform engineers&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Drive best practices in software design, reliability, security, and observability&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead technical discussions, review designs, and mentor team members&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
